Tony Okafor, Awka A former President and Chief Executive Officer of Transnational Corporation of Nigeria Plc, Valentine Ozigbo, has said he is in the Anambra State 2021 governorship contest to win. He explained that he wasn’t intimidated by the presence of the ex-governor of the Central Bank of Nigeria, Professor Chukwuma Soludo. Ozigbo said this in virtual press conference  with members of the Nigeria Union of Journalists, Anambra State council in Awka on Thursday. The aspirant who is seeking for the ticket of the Peoples Democratic Party, said, “If my party gives me its governorship ticket, and Soludo emerges in APGA or any other party, I will floor him.” Copyright PUNCH.
